        "paragraph":"The theme page is comprised of multiple blocks, each containing a specific functionality or design feature. "
      },
      {
        "id":2,
        "type":"text",
        "paragraph":"Some blocks have their own scripts included in the page source. These scripts are required at the moment the <span class=\"ttip\" data-attribute=\"Liquid\">liquid</span> code is parsed."
      },
      {
        "id":3,
        "type":"warning",
        "paragraph":"Do not move in-line or script snippet code from a block to a main collection javascript file. If the code is in the block, there's a good reason for that."
      },
      {
        "id":4,
        "type":"text",
        "paragraph":"It is important to note that all blocks have their own style constraints. When designing new blocks, refer to the parents' style constraints."
